- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Formal Verification) is a possibility as the paper uses a constructive and tight proof to derive the lower bounds. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a possibility as the paper deals with matrix-matrix multiplication, which is a common numerical operation. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is a possibility as the paper proposes a new algorithm for matrix-matrix multiplication that outperforms existing algorithms.
